KL MPhUrSTh PhUrSH VShS'yTh ShS'y PhUrSTh M'yLTh GUrH BBHMH 'aThH Th'aKLV.
'aK 'aTh-ZH L'a Th'aKLV MM'yLY HGUrH VMMPhUrSY HPhUrSH 'aTh-HGML KY-M'yLH GUrH HV'a VPhUrSH 'aYNNV MPhUrYS TM'a HV'a LKM.
V'aTh-HShPhN KY-M'yLH GUrH HV'a VPhUrSH L'a YPhUrYS TM'a HV'a LKM.
V'aTh-H'aUrNBTh KY-M'yLTh GUrH HV'a VPhUrSH L'a HPhUrYSH TM'aH HV'a LKM.
V'aTh-HChZYUr KY-MPhUrYS PhUrSH HV'a VShS'y ShS'y PhUrSH VHV'a GUrH L'a-YGUr TM'a HV'a LKM.
MBShUrM L'a Th'aKLV VBNBLThM L'a ThG'yV TM'aYM HM LKM.
'aTh-ZH Th'aKLV MKL 'aShUr BMYM KL 'aShUr-LV SNPhYUr VQShQShTh BMYM BYMYM VBNChLYM 'aThM Th'aKLV.
VKL 'aShUr 'aYN-LV SNPhYUr VQShQShTh BYMYM VBNChLYM MKL ShUrTSh HMYM VMKL NPhSh HChYH 'aShUr BMYM ShQTSh HM LKM.
VShQTSh YHYV LKM MBShUrM L'a Th'aKLV V'aTh-NBLThM ThShQTShV.
