V'aTh-HThNShMTh V'aTh-HQ'aTh V'aTh-HUrChM.
V'aTh HChSYDH H'aNPhH LMYNH V'aTh-HDVKYPhTh V'aTh-H'yTLPh.
KL ShUrTSh H'yVPh HHLK 'yL-'aUrB'y ShQTSh HV'a LKM.
'aK 'aTh-ZH Th'aKLV MKL ShUrTSh H'yVPh HHLK 'yL-'aUrB'y 'aShUr-L'a KUr'yYM MM'yL LUrGLYV LNThUr BHN 'yL-H'aUrTSh.
'aTh-'aLH MHM Th'aKLV 'aTh-H'aUrBH LMYNV V'aTh-HSL'yM LMYNHV V'aTh-HChUrGL LMYNHV V'aTh-HChGB LMYNHV.
VKL ShUrTSh H'yVPh 'aShUr-LV 'aUrB'y UrGLYM ShQTSh HV'a LKM.
VL'aLH ThTM'aV KL-HNG'y BNBLThM YTM'a 'yD-H'yUrB.
VKL-HNSh'a MNBLThM YKBS BGDYV VTM'a 'yD-H'yUrB.
LKL-HBHMH 'aShUr HV'a MPhUrSTh PhUrSH VShS'y 'aYNNH ShS'yTh VGUrH 'aYNNH M'yLH TM'aYM HM LKM KL-HNG'y BHM YTM'a.
VKL HVLK 'yL-KPhYV BKL-HChYH HHLKTh 'yL-'aUrB'y TM'aYM HM LKM KL-HNG'y BNBLThM YTM'a 'yD-H'yUrB.
